       Identification Division.
       Program-Id.                                 mcvoj0             .
      *================================================================*
      *                                                                *
      * Modulo per la gestione dei files line sequential in output per *
      * le conversioni                                                 *
      *                                                                *
      * Per tipo runtime : Acucobol 85                                 *
      *                                                                *
      * N.B.: e' uguale all'interfaccia 'mcvo00' ma sopperisce alla    *
      *       carenza strutturale di alcuni campi di 'g'               *
      *                                                                *
      * ============================================================== *
      *                                                                *
      * Tipi operazione previsti :                                     *
      *                                                                *
      *             -------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * Open Out    Open output line sequential file                   *
      *                                                                *
      *             Input  : j-ope = "OO"                              *
      *                                                                *
      *                      j-nam = file name                         *
      *                                                                *
      *                      j-pat = file pathname                     *
      *                                                                *
      *             Output : j-sts = Cobol i-o status                  *
      *                                                                *
      *             -------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * Open Ext    Open extend line sequential file                   *
      *                                                                *
      *             Input  : j-ope = "OE"                              *
      *                                                                *
      *                      j-nam = file name                         *
      *                                                                *
      *                      j-pat = file pathname                     *
      *                                                                *
      *             Output : j-sts = Cobol i-o status                  *
      *                                                                *
      *             -------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * Put Next    Put next record to line sequential file            *
      *                                                                *
      *             Input  : j-ope = "PN"                              *
      *                                                                *
      *                      j-rec = file record                       *
      *                                                                *
      *             Output : j-sts = Cobol i-o status                  *
      *                                                                *
      *             -------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * Close       Close line sequential file                         *
      *                                                                *
      *             Input  : j-ope = "CL"                              *
      *                                                                *
      *             Output : j-sts = Cobol i-o status                  *
      *                                                                *
      *             -------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      *================================================================*

      ******************************************************************
       Environment Division.
      ******************************************************************

      *================================================================*
       Configuration Section.
      *================================================================*

       Source-Computer.     d-K-b-Snc-PD .
       Object-Computer.     d-K-b-Snc-PD .

       Special-Names.       Decimal-Point is comma .

      *================================================================*
       Input-Output Section.
      *================================================================*

       File-Control.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Control [lsf]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           select            lsf   assign to input-output   f-lsf-pat
                             organization is line sequential
                             access  mode is sequential
                             file  status is                f-lsf-sts .

      ******************************************************************
       Data Division.
      ******************************************************************

      *================================================================*
       File Section.
      *================================================================*

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Description [lsf]                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       fd  lsf  label record omitted.
       01  lsf-rec.
           05  lsf-chr        occurs 5120 pic  x(01)                  .

      *================================================================*
       Working-Storage Section.
      *================================================================*

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Area ausiliaria per controllo i-o su [lsf]                *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       01  f-lsf.
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * File name                                             *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  f-lsf-nam                  pic  x(04) value spaces     .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * File pathname                                         *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  f-lsf-pat                  pic  x(80) value spaces     .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * File status                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  f-lsf-sts                  pic  x(02) value "00"       .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Area per definizione codici di errore di i-o              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "swd/mod/int/e"                                  .

      *================================================================*
       Linkage Section.
      *================================================================*

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Area di comunicazione per moduli di input-output su files *
      *    * di tipo line sequential                                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "swd/mod/int/j"                                  .

      ******************************************************************
       Procedure Division                using j                      .
      ******************************************************************

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Declaratives                                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       Declaratives.
       Decl Section.
           Use after standard error procedure on lsf                  .
       decl-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Traslazione del codice di i-o status contenuto  *
      *              * in f-lsf-sts nel codice di i-o status conven-   *
      *              * zionale                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/miosts"
                                         using f-lsf                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Spostamento cobol-file-status in area per defi- *
      *              * nizione codici di errore di i-o                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      f-lsf-sts            to   e-sts                  .
       End Declaratives.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Main program                                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       Main Section.
       main-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del tipo operazione      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        j-ope                =    "OO"
                     perform opn-out-000  thru opn-out-999
           else if   j-ope                =    "OE"
                     perform opn-ext-000  thru opn-ext-999
           else if   j-ope                =    "PN"
                     perform put-nxt-000  thru put-nxt-999
           else if   j-ope                =    "CL"
                     perform cls-cls-000  thru cls-cls-999            .
       main-999.
           exit      program.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Open output                                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       opn-out-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file name                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      j-nam                to   f-lsf-nam              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file pathname                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      j-pat                to   f-lsf-pat              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione open output                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione cobol i-o status            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "00"                 to   e-sts                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Operazione di i-o                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           open      output lsf                                       .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Spostamento cobol i-o status in uscita          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-sts                to   j-sts                  .
       opn-out-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Open extend                                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       opn-ext-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file name                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      j-nam                to   f-lsf-nam              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file pathname                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      j-pat                to   f-lsf-pat              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione open extend                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione cobol i-o status            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "00"                 to   e-sts                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Operazione di i-o                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           open      extend lsf                                       .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Spostamento cobol i-o status in uscita          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-sts                to   j-sts                  .
       opn-ext-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Put next                                                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       put-nxt-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione put next                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Spostamento record in entrata in area file  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      j-rec                to   lsf-rec                .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione cobol i-o status            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "00"                 to   e-sts                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Operazione di i-o                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           write     lsf-rec                                          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Spostamento cobol i-o status in uscita          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-sts                to   j-sts                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Spostamento record in uscita                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      lsf-rec              to   j-rec                  .
       put-nxt-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Close                                                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cls-cls-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione close                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione cobol i-o status            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "00"                 to   e-sts                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Operazione di i-o                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           close     lsf                                              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Spostamento cobol i-o status in uscita          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-sts                to   j-sts                  .
       cls-cls-999.
           exit.
